#churn:914 (chrun_free + churn_paid)

Accuracy rates from 3 classification models:
SVM
Prediction accuracy = 0.904693140794

Logistic regression
Prediction accuracy = 0.910469314079
 
Decision tree
Prediction accuracy = 0.906137184116

I will use features from logistic regression to explain datasets (since it got the highest accuracy rate) 

Characters of free churners
1. The churners use app for a longer period of time than active users
2. Get higher numbers of matched campaigns
3. Receive higher number of push.
4. Use older version of app
5. Allow push and feature push. Then revoke push afterward (on the same day as first use date. )
6. Sign in 

Characters of active and free users
1. Have more up to date SDK
2. Use more update version of the app
3. Allow Bluetooth
4. Answer more questions correctly

